hwSecStatGlobal.name: hwSecStatGlobal

revisions.description: V1.17 add a hwSecStatDeviceLoggedPackets table node.
V1.16 modify the hwSecStatSecPolicyRateTable table node.
V1.12, modify the MAX-ACCESS of the hwSecStatSecHittedVsysName and hwSecStatSecHittedRuleName node .
V1.11, modify the syntax type of the hwSecStatFragRate node from octet string to Integer32 .
V1.05, modify the description of the service-quality statistic node .
V1.06, modify the description of the service-quality statistic node .
V1.07, modify the MAX-ACCESS of the hwSecStatInterzoneSessTable node .
V1.08, modify the type of the service-quality node .
V1.09, modify the node of the hwSecStatPktRateObjects node .
V1.10, modify the node of the hwSecStatPktRateObjects node .
